  <Docs>
    <summary>Describes a Vulkan YCbCr sampler conversion for use with Skia GPU backends.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`GRVkYcbcrConversionInfo` describes a Vulkan YCbCr sampler conversion that enables Skia to
sample from a YCbCr Vulkan image. It corresponds to `VkSamplerYcbcrConversionCreateInfo`
and is used when creating a backend texture or image that references a YCbCr image plane.

Each numeric field holds a Vulkan enum value represented as a `uint` (e.g., `VkFormat`,
`VkSamplerYcbcrModelConversion`, `VkSamplerYcbcrRange`, `VkChromaLocation`, `VkFilter`).
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
